######## Anaconda Installation in ubuntu ####################


1. Download latest version of Anaconda installer(Anaconda3-2020.02-Linux-x86_64.sh)

2. Verify DataIntegrity of the Installer
   $ sha256sum Anaconda3-2020.02-Linux-x86_64.sh
   You will get out like this (2b9f088b2022edb474915d9f69a803d6449d5fdb4c303041f60ac4aefcc208bb  Anaconda3-2020.02-Linux-x86_64.sh)
   Verify the code is same from website(https://docs.anaconda.com/anaconda/install/hashes/Anaconda3-2020.02-Linux-x86_64.sh-hash/)

3. Run Anaconda Script
   $ bash Anaconda3-2020.02-Linux-x86_64.sh

   It will print below content
   Welcome to Anaconda3 2020.02

   In order to continue the installation process, please review the license
   agreement.
   Please, press ENTER to continue
   >>> 
   After ENTER you will get the license terms and type YES

4. Anaconda3 will now be installed into this location:
   /home/darkknight/anaconda3

   - Press ENTER to confirm the location
   - Press CTRL-C to abort the installation
   - Or specify a different location below

   Press Enter

5. Preparing transaction: done
   Executing transaction: done
   installation finished.
   Do you wish the installer to initialize Anaconda3
   by running conda init?

   Press YES

   Thank you for installing Anaconda3!


6. Activate Installation
   $  source ~/.bashrc (Generally terminal starts with non interactive login. This command is needed to login bash)

7. conda (used to manage environments of python, Anaconda)
   conda list
   conda info
   conda update conda
   conda update anaconda

